<h1>About The Lakes of Desolation</h1>
<p>The Lakes of Desolation is a website dedicated to the lakes of Desolation Wilderness. A personal project for Mike Mullen who grew up at Lake Tahoe near the wilderness area.</p>

<div class="mainquote">It is a way I have of driving off the spleen, and regulating the circulation. Whenever I find myself growing grim about the mouth; whenever it is a damp, drizzly November in my soul; whenever I find myself involuntarily pausing before coffin warehouses, and bringing up the rear of every funeral I meet; and especially whenever my hypos get such an upper hand of me, that it requires a strong moral principle to prevent me from deliberately stepping into the street, and methodically knocking people's hats off--then, I account it high time to get to sea as soon as I can.</div>